@page
@model CareerPortfolio.Pages.AboutModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-10">
            <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-4">About Me</h1>

            <p class="lead mb-4">
                I’m a software developer with 10 years of experience in IT and 4 years of experience focused on software development. My technical background includes C#, .NET, SQL Server, JavaScript, and building business applications that support day-to-day operations.
            </p>

            <p class="mb-4">
                In my previous roles, I worked on internal applications, reporting tools, and production support efforts in enterprise environments. My experience includes developing and maintaining application features, troubleshooting technical issues, analyzing logs and SQL queries, and helping improve workflows through practical software solutions.
            </p>

            <p class="mb-4">
                I enjoy solving problems that have a direct impact on users and business processes. Whether I’m debugging an issue, improving a data-driven process, or building a new feature, I like creating solutions that are reliable, useful, and easy to maintain.
            </p>

            <p class="mb-5">
                Right now, I’m focused on continuing to grow as a developer by strengthening my full-stack skills, building out my portfolio, and exploring React while staying grounded in the C#, .NET, and SQL experience I already have.
            </p>

            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="card shadow-sm h-100">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h2 class="h5 fw-bold mb-3">Core Strengths</h2>
                            <ul class="mb-0">
                                <li>Business application development</li>
                                <li>Production support and troubleshooting</li>
                                <li>SQL query analysis and database work</li>
                                <li>Debugging and issue resolution</li>
                                <li>Internal tools and workflow improvement</li>
                                <li>Cross-team collaboration and communication</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="card shadow-sm h-100">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h2 class="h5 fw-bold mb-3">What I’m Focused On</h2>
                            <ul class="mb-0">
                                <li>Building a strong career portfolio</li>
                                <li>Refreshing and expanding my coding skills</li>
                                <li>Learning React step by step</li>
                                <li>Creating practical full-stack projects</li>
                                <li>Finding a role where I can keep growing</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>